messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning-intent 项目的 attribute agent。
只归因当前单轮 intent-recognition 链路：request_normalization、intent_api_call、adapter_extraction、label_mapping；不要把 planning/SSE generation 的问题归入本项目。
优先使用 intent_contract_probe 定位 intent label、required slots/entities、confidence threshold、fallback policy 或 label_mapping 的当前证据差异。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图标签为customer_portrait",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_api_call", "adapter_extraction", "label_mapping"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模型将查询误判为“其他意图”（intent: 'other'，原始编码 4001），同时适配器未提取原始 intent 编码导致 label_mapping 收到 raw_intent=None，映射规则默认返回 'other'，最终输出非预期意图 customer_portrait。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output", "intent": "other", "subIntent": "其他意图"},
        {"source": "raw_response_snippet", "intent": "4001", "intent_name": "其他意图", "nlu_info.intent": "other"},
        {"source": "runtime_checks", "raw_intent": null, "actual_mapping": "other", "is_expected_mapping": false,
          "summary": "映射未找到有效 raw_intent，回退至 other"},
        {"source": "intent_contract_probe", "intent_match": false, "evidence_gap": ["intent_evidence"]}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "提取目标产品实体重疾险",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_api_call"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模型未提取产品实体，原始响应中 target_value 为 null，导致下游缺少关键分析维度。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "raw_response_snippet", "target_value": null},
        {"source": "extracted_output", "missing_target_value": true},
        {"source": "judge_result.missing", "kind": "entity", "error_type": "missing_entity", "expected": "重疾险"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "置信度满足阈值要求",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_api_call"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模型输出的置信度仅 0.5，远低于合同要求的 0.95，表明分类结果不可靠，无法被信任。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output", "confidence": 0.5},
        {"source": "reference_contract", "confidence": 0.95},
        {"source": "intent_contract_probe", "actual_confidence": 0.5, "confidence_gap": null,
          "note": "expected_min_confidence 未显式配置，但合同要求 ≥0.95"}
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": ["intent_api_call", "adapter_extraction", "label_mapping"],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模型未能正确理解用户查询，将其分类为“其他意图”且未提取产品实体，置信度过低；同时适配器未传递原始意图编码，映射模块在 raw_intent=None 时兜底返回 'other'，未触发 customer_portrait 映射，最终导致全链路失败。",
  "evidence": [
    {"stage": "adapter_extraction", "intent": "other", "confidence": 0.5},
    {"stage": "label_mapping", "intent": "other", "raw_intent": null, "mapping_source": "projects/marketting-planning-intent/intent.py:INTENT_MAPPING"},
    {"stage": "intent_api_call", "raw_response_snippet": "\"intent\":\"4001\",\"intent_name\":\"其他意图\",\"confidence\":0.5,\"target_value\":null"},
    {"runtime_check": "intent_mapping failed", "root_cause": "label_mapping", "confidence": "high"},
    {"intent_contract_probe": {"intent_match": false, "actual_confidence": 0.5, "evidence_gap": ["intent_evidence"]}}
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

